videos.headline: Colorado QB gets annihilated on flea flicker
videos.description: Colorado QB Stephen Montez gets hit hard on a flea flicker by Colin Schooler for a loss of 13 yards.

videos.headline: Arizona WR fights pass interference to grab 40-yard TD
videos.description: QB Khalil Tate heaves a 40-yard pass into the end zone where Stanley Berryhill III fights off a pass interference call for the touchdown.

videos.headline: Colorado goes back in front with 57-yard TD
videos.description: Travon McMillian reels in a pass over two defenders and takes it to the house to give Colorado a 24-23 lead.

videos.headline: Colorado regains lead again on Montez's 3rd TD
videos.description: QB Steven Montez drops in dime in the back of the end zone to retake the lead once again, 31-26.

videos.headline: Arizona WR beats two defenders to put them back on top
videos.description: Shawn Poindexter gets behind two defenders to make a diving catch into the end zone, putting Arizona back in front at 32-31.
